Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.83,0:00:09.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:12.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.92,0:00:16.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:24.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.89,0:00:34.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:41.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.99,0:00:48.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.95,0:00:56.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.09,0:00:59.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:03.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.47,0:01:07.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.47,0:01:10.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:14.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:18.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.19,0:01:21.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.19,0:01:25.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:29.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.41,0:01:32.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:35.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.71,0:01:41.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:49.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go follow Franky?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:02:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drat. Looks like they really\Ndon't know where the money is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we strangle this Franky guy,\Nif he already spent the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do now? Even if we wait for\Nhim here, he won't be back for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Staying here talking won't get us anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.04,0:02:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to the ship for now.\NWe left Nami-san alone there, too, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have the thing with\NRobin-chan to deal with...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the issues with the ship, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's say goodbye... to the Going Merry here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:52.86,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Big Fight under the Moon!\NThe Pirate Flag Flutters with Sorrow!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.91,0:02:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:02:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Usopp woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.75,0:03:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can relax a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan isn't back yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, don't worry us so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. To think that you marched\Nin by yourself... That was so reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were lucky that you didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think a little before you act.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because I'm so good-for-nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.29,0:03:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really... I'm ashamed! Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That money was so crucial to\Nus and yet, I let it... I let it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.89,0:03:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold on a sec! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I get it, so let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:04:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... the huge amount of money we got,\Nafter all that we went through...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, you should still be in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen to Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, as I was afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the money won't come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we won't know for sure\Nuntil this Franky guy comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, even if we don't get it back,\Nwe still have the 100 million Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's okay. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not okay about the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.51,0:04:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami...\N--Ah... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Luffy... What about the ship?\NWhat about the Merry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we somehow have her repaired\Nwith that remaining 100 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're lucky that we can have her\Nrepaired in such a first-class shipyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order for her to be able to travel in\Nthe seas ahead, I'd like her to be stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want her to be repaired perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, does it look like those guys will\Nrepair her if we pay 100 million Berries?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, about the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to get a new ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.22,0:05:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that I made the\Ndecision without consulting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've already made my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.35,0:05:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Going Merry took good care of us,\Nbut our journey with her ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took a look at the catalogue\Nthat Ice pops gave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While checking the ships in it, I noticed\Nthat there're quite a few kinds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get a used one, 100 million will\Nallow us to buy a bigger ship than Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:06:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Wait a sec. You're taking\Nthe joke too far. That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Chopper took it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what'll we do with our captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something to him, Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... does that mean that we don't\Nhave enough money for the repair?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I got that 200 million stolen by them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,w-we're now short on money, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's what's going on, right, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.67,0:06:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cost of a first-class shipyard\Nwould also be first-class, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?! Spit it out! Are you\Ntrying to be considerate to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not! It has nothing to do\Nwith that money being stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you saying stupid stuff\Nlike that we're gonna get a new ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What good will fighting do?\NCalm down and talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I calm down when he\Nstarts saying stupid stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! This is an important matter.\NDon't get so worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right, Usopp. You need\Nto rest, or you won't get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about my body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I be quiet when our captain\Ncasually says we'll get a new ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not casual! I made the\Ndecision after agonizing over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What and how did you agonize over\Nto make this kind of decision?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you talk about it\Nwhile waving this stupid thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy, if it wasn't because we\Ngot our money stolen, then why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, why don't you say it?! Hey!\NWhy are you keeping quiet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not being considerate\Nto me, then don't hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it! I won't accept it unless\NI hear good reason! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Merry can no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.59,0:08:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me repeat myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Merry can no longer be repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what we do, she won't be fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I wouldn't say something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship?! Are you talking about this\Nship that we're on board right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. This ship will sink soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.03,0:08:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth. They told us at the shipyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that she can't\Neven reach the next island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really... She can't, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were persuaded by\Nstrangers you just met today
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and gave up just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.76,0:08:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because first-class\Nshipwrights told you that this is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you gave up just like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've traveled together all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it through all sorts\Nof waves and battles together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's our dear friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna abandon her in a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how little this ship means to you, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't shout like that, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sorry, but step aside.\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done talking with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.63,0:09:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then can you make an accurate assessment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a shipwright on this ship.\NThat's why we asked them to check her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! We don't have to\Nask those guys to fix her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll repair her, as I always have!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how we've continued\Nto travel in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's start now. Hey, help me, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,0:09:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, we don't have enough lumber.\NI'll go buy some at the shipyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we're getting busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a shipwright, are you, Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right. So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't trust irresponsible\Nshipwrights who easily give up on a ship
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.97,0:10:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just because it belongs to someone else
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by taking advantage of\Ntheir position as craftsmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be a lesson that we should\Nprotect our own ship by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never... give up on this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys stupid or what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably got fooled by the shipwrights'\Nconvincing argument, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Luffy I know would've believed\Nin the strength of the Merry first
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,rather than buying those guys' sales talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a clear-cut answer that sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like one made by an old man\Nwho understands everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you make a decision like that,\Nsuddenly acting all captain-like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I misjudged you, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.05,0:10:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec, Usopp! Luffy, too, first--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of this, Nami!\NThis is something I decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't change my opinion.\NNo matter what you say now,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.85,0:11:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're gonna get a new ship!\NWe'll say goodbye to the Merry here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous! I won't allow that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Luffy! It's not like everyone\Ncan live looking ahead like you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just leave our wounded friend\Nhere and move on to the seas ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous! Even if she's a friend,\Nships and humans are different!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the same! Merry has\Nthe strength to live left in her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Considering how you are, aren't you\Nexcited thinking about the new ship\N--Hey, that's enough, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--while pretending to be concerned about Merry?!\N--You can't have a conversation\Nif you're worked up like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that you're the only\None who feels pain over this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone feels the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.47,0:11:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, there's no way you'd\Ndecide to get a new ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! If you dislike what I decide\Nthat much, then get off this--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot... What were you about to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:12:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool down! Be careful about\Nwhat you say! Got that, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay, Luffy. That's how\Nyou really feel, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and cut off useless friends\None after another and move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna abandon the Merry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why don't you do that to me, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and cut off useless friends\None after another and move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:13:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna abandon the Merry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why don't you do that to me, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Usopp. Don't say stupid stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about this for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking that I can't keep\Nup with your monstrous strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like today... I can't even watch over money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just keep causing you guys trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need weak friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... you're the man\Nwho'll be king of the pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have to go that high up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking back, when I was about to sail out,\Nyou guys asked me to join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talkin' about? Get on already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:14:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends now, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all that's tying us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.83,0:14:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to travel together\Nwhen we have a difference of opinion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where're you going, Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where I'm going is my own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with you guys anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...leaving the gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.34,0:14:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What're you doing, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay to let him go like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:14:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Go after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've come this far together.\NIs it okay to part like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp is our precious friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy... You are the captain, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.68,0:15:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! It shouldn't be like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go! Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:16:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! I can't go along with you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.39,0:16:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to cause you trouble until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that the ship\Nbelongs to you, the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So fight me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight a duel with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:17:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? Er, hey... what're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At 10 o'clock tonight, I'll come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll fight a duel over the Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat you and take the Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.77,0:17:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the end of the bond\Nbetween you guys and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?! Stop this nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to fight\Na duel with your friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you give it a little time,\Nyou two will cool down, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, too. He just got flared up\Nbecause things were moving quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we've come this far, we can't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can apologize to him and talk it over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:18:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said... it's no longer possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp isn't stupid enough to risk\Nhis life under the influence of anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if talking it over\Nwould change his opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this wouldn't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get it, leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying, the Franky Family\Ncame here this afternoon, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you beat them\Nall up beyond recovery then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had, Usopp wouldn't have\Nbeen attacked and felt guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, instead of going shopping,\Nyou should've stayed and fought them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to get necessary food as your cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fighting at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been enough fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight over what's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.16,0:18:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san...! But this idiot is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper... Didn't you... go follow Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to continue treating his wounds,\Nbut he turned me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got a place to stay in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "You and I are no longer friends,\Nso go back to the ship!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that fun time up until this\Nmorning seems like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.83,0:19:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something is happening\Nto Robin on top of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like... the gang is falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.47,0:19:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.89,0:20:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I somehow feel restless tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 10 o'clock, the promised time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.69,0:20:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, don't leave the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There he is!\N--Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you didn't get cold feet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better be sure you're not going\Nto regret this, no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the duel you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.87,0:21:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. You'd better fight seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.59,0:21:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn the tables on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.46,0:21:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already figured out how to defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.69,0:22:09.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:12.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:18.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:20.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:23.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:29.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.13,0:22:32.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:34.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.01,0:22:37.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.80,0:22:40.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.89,0:22:43.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:46.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:52.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.19,0:22:55.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:57.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:00.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:08.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.34,0:23:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it. It's ridiculous for friends to fight a duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.30,0:23:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once what we protect becomes\Ndifferent, we're no longer friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.51,0:23:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over between us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.76,0:23:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that. Luffy, you restrain yourself, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.43,0:23:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely because we're all friends,\Nbe prepared and watch quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.85,0:23:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy vs. Usopp! Collision of Two Men's Pride"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.90,0:23:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
